{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMultiPolygon(cm)multiPolygonWithPolygons:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"instancetype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSArray<MLNPolygon *>","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"polygons","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"polygons","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The array of polygons defining the shape.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Return Value","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"return-value"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A new multipolygon object.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Creates and returns a multipolygon object consisting of the given polygons."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/multipolygonwithpolygons:"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/multiPolygonWithPolygons:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon/multiPolygonWithPolygons:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/multipolygonwithpolygons:","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/multiPolygonWithPolygons:","abstract":[{"text":"Creates and returns a multipolygon object consisting of the given polygons.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon":{"title":"MLNMultiPolygon","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolygon"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polygons that do not overlap. For example, you could use a multipolygon shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll: the inner island would be one "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object, while the surrounding"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group of disconnected but related buildings."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolygon":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","type":"topic","title":"MLNPolygon","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a closed shape consisting of four or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"vertices, specified as "},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the edges that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use a polygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"building, a lake, or an area you want to highlight."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolygon","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"title":"MapLibre"}}}